you should stop being mad.

44:18.209 --> 44:20.129
I think Lord Qin...

44:20.488 --> 44:20.968
No.

44:21.209 --> 44:23.368
I mean he's apologizing to you
sincerely this time.

44:23.808 --> 44:24.888
Didn't he say

44:25.049 --> 44:26.649
that he wasn't supposed to trust you?

44:27.808 --> 44:29.129
Actually, Cui Li was the one

44:29.328 --> 44:31.089
behind Young Master's passing.

44:31.529 --> 44:32.808
It's not his fault.

44:33.808 --> 44:34.848
Strange.

44:35.169 --> 44:36.488
Why are you

44:36.848 --> 44:38.249
speaking up for him today?

44:38.928 --> 44:39.928
Lieutenant He,

44:40.249 --> 44:42.209
I'm doing this for your sake.

44:42.768 --> 44:44.089
I think Lord Qin

44:44.249 --> 44:46.129
is truly nice to you.

44:46.368 --> 44:48.768
