45:08.649 --> 45:09.488
But...

45:12.448 --> 45:13.490
To me, he's different from

45:14.649 --> 45:16.209
other people.

45:20.129 --> 45:21.729
I see.

45:22.649 --> 45:24.129
I was wondering why.

45:25.320 --> 45:26.700
I'll get angry if you keep that up.

45:28.089 --> 45:28.689
It's my fault.

45:28.848 --> 45:29.569
Don't be angry.

45:30.129 --> 45:31.400
I'll change your flowers for you.

